Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:07.34,EN,,0,0,0,,The expectations of boys and girls who exposed their bare feet and broke into a run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.55,0:00:11.73,EN,,0,0,0,,Since it is fine too to be wet with water after this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:19.81,EN,,0,0,0,,A blinding argument tautologically. Oh, another day was closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:24.35,EN,,0,0,0,,An altogether fabricated sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:31.30,EN,,0,0,0,,The emotions that were pressing against our chests at that time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:38.81,EN,,0,0,0,,And the tears we shed. What is the expiration date for tears that one was lured by?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.34,0:00:43.90,EN,,0,0,0,,A certain future. The future we are laughing together about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:50.68,EN,,0,0,0,,If it had been the future of several days later
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:58.98,EN,,0,0,0,,Is tomorrow that you harbor not bitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:05.30,EN,,0,0,0,,Draw one line on the letters that are squirming in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.30,0:01:11.25,EN,,0,0,0,,Can the today that you harbor not be saved at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:17.96,EN,,0,0,0,,Even so, if I loaded kindness onto those shoulders,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.96,0:01:24.94,EN,,0,0,0,,Would you be able to feel love again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:42.40,EN,,0,0,0,,Did I have magic be cast on me that was leniently omitted, you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:46.78,EN,,0,0,0,,Can it not be undone by anyone, you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:54.87,EN,,0,0,0,,In the case of a situation that grew unforgivable for things also that were forgivable,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:59.48,EN,,0,0,0,,It is not like only words will become words.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:30.85,EN,,0,0,0,,Even if those several seconds are destined,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:36.69,EN,,0,0,0,,Even if those several steps are destined,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:43.67,EN,,0,0,0,,Is stopping that determination being selfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:46.00,EN,,0,0,0,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:49.73,EN,,0,0,0,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:52.49,EN,,0,0,0,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:59.21,EN,,0,0,0,,Now--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:05.15,EN,,0,0,0,,Is the spot that you were aiming for not dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:11.46,EN,,0,0,0,,If I assume that it is the mere shadow of a big light,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:17.69,EN,,0,0,0,,I do not want to make you go to the place where you begin your trip;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:24.17,EN,,0,0,0,,For example, even if you sleep quietly beyond that point,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:28.54,EN,,0,0,0,,Even if you assume that it is your happiness--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:33.21,EN,,0,0,0,,Is your tomorrow not bitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:39.40,EN,,0,0,0,,Draw one line on the letters that are squirming in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:45.81,EN,,0,0,0,,Can the today that you harbor not be saved at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:52.19,EN,,0,0,0,,Even so, if I loaded kindness onto those shoulders,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:59.52,EN,,0,0,0,,Would you be able to feel love again?
